diff:1619235963:1619235963:=1,72d0%0a%3c (:if authgroup @tas:)%0a%3c %0a%3c (:toggle id=gi show="show grading interface" hide="hide grading interface":)%0a%3c %0a%3c >>id=gi%3c%3c%0a%3c %0a%3c [[GradebookArticles.{$Name}|See article in gradebook]] \\%0a%3c [[{$FullName}?action=diff|See all changes to article]]%0a%3c %0a%3c (:foxform Site.FoxForms#gradeitem:)%0a%3c %0a%3c (:foxform Site.FoxForms#gradingcomment:)%0a%3c %0a%3c >>%3c%3c%0a%3c %0a%3c ----%0a%3c %0a%3c (:ifend:)%0a%3c %0a%3c [[!LinguisticDiscriminationInTheWild]]%0a%3c %0a%3c !Linguistic Discrimination against "aight" in BVE%0a%3c %0a%3c :Author: nithyas%0a%3c %0a%3c '''Summary:''' \\%0a%3c %0a%3c [[#summary]]%0a%3c %0a%3c One PhD Quora user suggests "aight" is not a real word%0a%3c %0a%3c [[#summaryends]]%0a%3c %0a%3c ----%0a%3c [[#content]]%0a%3c %0a%3c Black Vernacular English is often the target of linguistic discrimination and is perceived as a dialect spoken by the uneducated. Many believe that BVE “sounds less intelligent” and is just an improperly spoken version of Standard American English. Various words and phrases in BVE have been criticized for being ungrammatical. One example of a word from this dialect is “aight”, which has transcription [ˈaˌɐɪt], and this Quora user, who actually has a PhD in English, claims that “aight” is not a real word and does not meet the standards to be considered a real word. %0a%3c %0a%3c The original transcription of the word is [ɔːlˈɹaɪt]. As we can see, there is the medial consonant deletion (of [l] and [ɹ]) as well as the diphthongization of the first vowel in the sentence (the length of the vowel sound is extended and is characterized by two different vowel sounds put together). Finally, the change from /ɔ/ to /a/ and /ɐ/ also involves a change in the backness of the vowel. Namely, the “ungrammatical” version changes the first vowel in the word to be more to the front than the vowel in the conventional pronunciation. Thus, the criticisms of the use of “aight” instead of “alright” are criticisms of the above phenomena.  %0a%3c %0a%3c Link to example: https://www.quora.com/Do-you-consider-aight-to-be-a-word %0a%3c %0a%3c %0a%3c [[#contentends]]%0a%3c ----%0a%3c ----%0a%3c %0a%3c !!Expansions:%0a%3c [[#expansions]]%0a%3c %0a%3c [[#expansionsend]]%0a%3c %0a%3c ----%0a%3c %25red%25 '''Add an expansion:'''%0a%3c %0a%3c (:if [ exists GradebookExpansions.{$Name}-{$Author} || equal {$Author} {$:Author} ] :)%0a%3c %0a%3c (:else:)%0a%3c %0a%3c (:foxform Site.FoxForms#newexpansion:)%0a%3c %0a%3c (:ifend:)%0a%3c %0a%3c ----%0a%3c ----%0a%3c %0a%3c !!Comments%0a%3c %0a%3c %0a%3c %0a%3c (:section: D:)%0a%3c (:Category: LinguisticDiscriminationInTheWild:)%0a\ No newline at end of file%0a
